article_id:2964,category_name:News,title_name:3.5-Year Anniversary Packs Are Here!,image_path:https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/f260a21a8222ad2e86453902d621e409.png,message:<div>Anniversary packs are available for a limited time under Value Packs in the Shop as of <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1648360800"></span>!</div><div><br></div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/f260a21a8222ad2e86453902d621e409.png"></div><div><br>■Availability Period<br><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1648360800"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1650002399"></span><br><br>Check out the details for each pack below.<br><br>■Anniversary Diamantium Mega-Pack<br>This pack contains diamantium.<br><br>&lt;Diamantium Included&gt;<br>・5,700 (3,920 + 1,780 bonus)<br><br>■Anniversary Sunlight Stone Quad-Pack<br>This pack contains diamantium and items useful for upgrading dragons.<br><br>&lt;Diamantium Included&gt;<br>・4,800 (3,920 + 880 bonus)<br>&lt;Other Items Included&gt;<br>・Sunlight Stone &times; 4<br><br>■Anniversary Unbind Pack<br>This pack contains diamantium and items useful for unbinding weapons, wyrmprints, and dragons, as well as items useful for unlocking mana circles.<br><br>&lt;Diamantium Included&gt;<br>・4,800 (3,920 + 880 bonus)<br>&lt;Other Items Included&gt;<br>・Knight&#39;s Testament &times; 1<br>・Champion&#39;s Testament &times; 1<br>・Rainbow Orb &times; 20<br>・Damascus Ingot &times; 1<br>・Adamantite Ingot &times; 1<br>・Golden Key &times; 1<br>・Sunlight Stone &times; 1<br><br>■Anniversary Superior Orb Pack<br>This pack contains diamantium and items useful for unlocking mana circles.<br><br>&lt;Diamantium Included&gt;<br>・2,400 (1,920 + 480 bonus)<br>&lt;Other Items Included&gt;<br>・Champion&#39;s Testament &times; 4<br>・Incandescence Orb &times; 50<br>・Tsunami Orb &times; 50<br>・Tempest Orb &times; 50<br>・Resplendence Orb &times; 50<br>・Abaddon Orb &times; 50<br>・Rainbow Orb &times; 50<br><br>Note: This product is not available in some countries/regions.<br><br>■Anniversary Diamantium Pack<br>This pack contains diamantium.<br><br>&lt;Diamantium&gt;<br>・1,200 (840 + 360 bonus)<br><br>Note: This product is not available in some countries/regions.<br><br>■Anniversary Facility Upgrade Special<br>This pack contains diamantium and items useful for leveling up facilities.<br><br>&lt;Diamantium Included&gt;<br>・960 (480 + 480 bonus)<br>&lt;Other Items Included&gt;<br>・Dyrenell Aureus &times; 500<br>・Royal Vermilion Insignia &times; 100<br>・Royal Azure Insignia &times; 100<br>・Royal Jade Insignia &times; 100<br>・Royal Amber Insignia &times; 100<br>・Royal Violet Insignia &times; 100<br><br>Note: This product is not available in some countries/regions.<br><br>■Anniversary Wind Unbind Special<br>A pack containing diamantium and items to assist with unlocking the mana circles of wind-attuned adventurers.<br><br>&lt;Diamantium&gt;<br>・700 (480 + 220 bonus)<br>&lt;Other&gt;<br>・Tempest Orb &times; 50<br>・Maelstrom Orb &times; 10<br>・Storm Orb &times; 30<br>・Wind Orb &times; 120<br>・Windwyrm&#39;s Squallscale &times; 40<br>・Windwyrm&#39;s Scale &times; 70<br>・Rainbow Orb &times; 10<br>・Champion&#39;s Testament &times; 1<br><br>Note: This product is not available in some countries/regions.<br><br>■Anniversary Light Unbind Special<br>A pack containing diamantium and items to assist with unlocking the mana circles of light-attuned adventurers.<br><br>&lt;Diamantium&gt;<br>・700 (480 + 220 bonus)<br>&lt;Other&gt;<br>・Resplendence Orb &times; 50<br>・Refulgence Orb &times; 10<br>・Radiance Orb &times; 30<br>・Light Orb &times; 120<br>・Lightwyrm&#39;s Glowscale &times; 40<br>・Lightwyrm&#39;s Scale &times; 70<br>・Rainbow Orb &times; 10<br>・Champion&#39;s Testament &times; 1<br><br>Note: This product is not available in some countries/regions.<br><br>■Anniversary Shadow Unbind Special<br>A pack containing diamantium and items to assist with unlocking the mana circles of shadow-attuned adventurers.<br><br>&lt;Diamantium&gt;<br>・700 (480 + 220 bonus)<br>&lt;Other&gt;<br>・Abaddon Orb &times; 50<br>・Nether Orb &times; 10<br>・Nightfall Orb &times; 30<br>・Shadow Orb &times; 120<br>・Shadowwyrm&#39;s Darkscale &times; 40<br>・Shadowwyrm&#39;s Scale &times; 70<br>・Rainbow Orb &times; 10<br>・Champion&#39;s Testament &times; 1<br><br>Note: This product is not available in some countries/regions.<br><br>Notes:<br>1. For information about each pack, select the Shop on the Home page, then select Anniversary Packs.<br>2. Each Anniversary pack may only be purchased once during the availability period.<br><br>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1648360800,update_time1646716507